pg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Taylor-Swift-Beyonce@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Taylor-Swift-Beyonce@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Taylor-Swift-Beyonce@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂斯</a>的粉丝们在社交媒体上猛烈抨击了他们各自巡演中提供的“遮挡视线”门票。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/beyonce-renaissance-review-tracklist-artwork-3278806">碧昂丝 - “文艺复兴”评论：爱与黑人欢乐的庆典</a></strong></li></ul><p>目前，两位流行歌星都开始在美国各地进行巡演——斯威夫特结束了她的<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/taylor-swifts-eras-tour-kick-off-top-five-moments-from-the-stars-transcendent-performance-3416005">“Eras”巡演</a>的北美站，而碧昂斯则演奏了她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-adds-fifth-and-final-london-date-to-2023-renaissance-tour-buy-tickets-3393877">“Renaissance”世界巡演</a>中列出的剩余节目。</p><p>这<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonces-renaissance-tour-could-make-500million-more-than-taylor-swifts-eras-tour-3441163">两场巡演都将成为有史以来票房最高的巡演之一</a>。 <a href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/petercohan/2023/05/08/beyonc-renaissance-tour-could-outearn-taylor-swift-eras-by-600-million/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《福布斯》</em></a>今年早些时候的一份报告预测，到 9 月份结束时，《文艺复兴》仅凭门票收入就可能达到 2.75 亿至 24 亿美元，其中《时代》预计将带来 19 亿美元的收入。</p><p>然而，一些粉丝对现场表演提供的“只听”和“阻碍观看”门票印象不深。这些门票因其在场馆中的位置而被标记为部分遮挡视野，并且通常以比其他门票更低的价格提供。</p><p>尽管如此，一些人很快就辩称，他们对这些座位的收费仍然过高，也就是说，在某些情况下，他们根本看不到舞台。</p><p>据<em><a href="https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/news/taylor-swift-beyonce-fans-no-view-tickets-b2386762.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《独立报》</a></em>报道，一些歌迷解释说，他们在斯威夫特最近的演出中花了大约 50 美元（38 英镑）购买“视野受阻”的座位，却发现这些座位位于主舞台的正后方，他们只能看到歌手当她走到人行道上时。</p><p> “你只能在最后一刻买到有遮挡的门票，但看到清洁车并向泰勒说再见是值得的，”其中一位写道，分享了她在斯威夫特最近的一场演出中看到的景色。另一位评论道：“我差点就买票了，直到我姐姐把它们击落，因为它们实际上就在屏幕后面。” </p><blockquote class="tiktok-embed" cite="https://www.tiktok.com/@annanallick/video/7249032057576312107" data-video-id="7249032057576312107" data-embed-from="oembed" style="max-width: 605px;min-width: 325px;" ><section> <a target="_blank" title="@annanallick" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@annanallick?refer=embed">@annanallick</a></p><p> The Eras Tour 没有不好的座位！在这里比在格伦代尔之夜 1 的地板上玩得更开心。 <a title="泰勒斯威夫特" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/taylorswift?refer=embed">#taylorswift</a> <a title="埃拉斯托尔" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/erastour?refer=embed">#erastour</a> <a title="泰罗尼亚" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/taylornation?refer=embed">#taylornation</a> <a title="斯威夫托克" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/swifttok?refer=embed">#swifttok</a> <a title="明尼阿波利斯时代之旅" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/minneapoliststheerastour?refer=embed">#minneapoliststheerastour</a></p><p> <a target="_blank" title="♬ 原声 - 安娜" href="https://www.tiktok.com/music/original-sound-7249032080342993707?refer=embed">♬ 原声 – 安娜</a></section></blockquote><p><script async src="https://www.tiktok.com/embed.js"></script></p><p> Another took to Twitter (X), to share their view of Beyoncé&#39;s concert, saying that they were “so disappointed” after getting that view of the stage after paying for floor tickets. They also claimed that they were not told that the view would be obstructed when they bought the tickets.</p><p> “Not me getting floor tickets to Beyonce and this monstrous thing is in my way… TF so disappointed. It did not say obstructed view.”</p><p> One also highlighted how some of the obstructed tickets were being made available on resale sites, and re-priced at over $700 (£552) each.</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> Not me getting floor tickets to Beyonce and this monstrous thing is in my way… <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f974.png" al